item.title: How do u change were u first spawn when u log in please tell me fast!
item.dc:creator: @hippyss hippyss
item.description:
@hippyss wrote:

Open up player.java, search // initial x and y coordinates of the player then put your coords on the teleportToX,teleportToY spots. then search // client initially doesn't know those values yet then change the absx and absy to your coords.
Also to change where you spawn when you die search IN client.javaOh dear you died! then look around there should be tome teleportTo things just change them as needed.
